      "review_text": "Love the game.\nOnly complaint so far is how many vhs's use the same art for different movies.\nLike in the Action section, atleast 5 movie covers have 2 dudes on it, but then there's an ice cream cone, or a register, or a balloon. But its the same two dudes in the exact same pose.\n\nOther than that, no real complaints.",
